He said that pill was extremely poisonous.

105
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,000
Indeed.

106
00:06:48,450 --> 00:06:49,340
But now,

107
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:51,900
I need to Shi Si to take the pill.

108
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:54,230
If the fragments are polluted by the poison of the demonic aura,

109
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,480
