114
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,000
But Doctor Toad said

115
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:09,500
Shi Si would die after taking it.

116
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,550
I'm here.

117
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:11,480
