149
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:20,580
how powerful I am.

150
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:23,040
We can do it.

151
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,300
People call me Fairy Fangfei.

152
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,810
So there must be something in me that distinguishes me from ordinary people.

153
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:30,030
I can always

154
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,130
achieve a lot effortlessly

155
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:32,840
and turn calamities into blessings.

156
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,309
But this is very dangerous.

157
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,710
I know.

158
00:08:37,179 --> 00:08:38,890
I think

159
00:08:39,299 --> 00:08:40,590
you must be one of those

160
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,350
who only make sacrifices for others

161
00:08:42,809 --> 00:08:44,890
and won't let others make sacrifices for you.

162
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,880
So this time,

163
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:48,690
just let Yan and I try our best to save you.

164
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,020
Shi Si.

165
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,800
Do you know

166
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,970
what the most important thing is to us now?

167
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:37,950
It's time.

168
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,120
If time allows,

169
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,750
I hope

170
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,470
none of us will have to take risks.

171
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:50,070
I'm willing to go everywhere

172
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:52,900
to find a perfect way to solve the problem.

173
00:09:58,490 --> 00:09:59,800
But

174
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,310
I don't want you

175
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:04,590
to sacrifice your lives to save mine.

176
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,950
Don't say that.

177
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:10,390
I want us to live and die together.

178
00:10:12,710 --> 00:10:14,390
Last time you blamed me

179
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:15,720
because I took action on my own

180
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,280
and fell into Demon Lord's trap.

181
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,560
This time, we'll take action together. Why won't you allow me to do that?

182
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:23,690
Stop joking.

183
00:10:24,380 --> 00:10:25,390
Okay.

184
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,720
Shi Si.

185
00:10:30,470 --> 00:10:31,070
Look at me.

186
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:37,070
I don't care how much time Demon Lord will give us.

187
00:10:38,090 --> 00:10:39,070
What I care about is

188
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,670
how much time you still have.

189
00:10:46,070 --> 00:10:47,710
I want to spend the rest of my life with you.

190
00:10:49,370 --> 00:10:51,060
And we won't have enough time to spend with each other if we don't do that.

191
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,680
You're the eldest son of the Mo family.

192
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,630
But you consider our love as the most important thing to you.

193
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,130
