263
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:24,300
Should I be shy?

264
00:16:26,620 --> 00:16:28,020
We know each other so well.

265
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:28,560
I don't need you to pretend to be shy.

266
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:29,480
You...

267
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:33,040
