268
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,840
In my eyes, you're a bossy and unreasonable young lady from a rich family.

269
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:40,670
And you're moody and arrogant

270
00:16:40,690 --> 00:16:41,970
